   <div class="lessonGroup" id="pluralAddIES">
    <h2>Nouns Ending in a consonant and '<span class="color3">y</span>'</h2>
    <p>For these nouns, remove the '<span class="color3">y</span>' and add '<span class="color3">ies</span>'.</p>
    <h4>Examples:</h4>
    <div class="examplesPluralAddIES">
     <p>
      berry <i class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-right"></i> berr<span class="color3">ies</span>
