   <div class="lessonGroup" id="pluralIrregular">
    <h2>Irregular Nouns</h2>
    <p>For these nouns, there are no rules to follow and you just have to memorize how to change them to the plural
     form.</p>
    <h4>Examples:</h4>
    <div class="examplesPluralIrregular">
     <p>
      <span class="color4">mouse </span><i class="fas fa-arrows-alt-h"></i><span class="color3"> mice</span>
     </p>
     <p>
      <span class="color4">tooth </span><i class="fas fa-arrows-alt-h"></i><span class="color3"> teeth</span>
